'''贝兹学院'''（{{lang-en|Bates College}} {{IPAc-en|ˈ|b|eɪ|t|s}}）或譯'''貝茨學院'''，是位于[[美国|美国]][[缅因州|缅因州]][[劉易斯頓_(緬因州)|劉易斯頓]]的私立[[美國文理學院|文理學院]]，由废奴主义者于1855年建成，是[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]地區第一所男女同校的大学。<ref>{{cite web | first =  | last =  | title = Coeducation | publisher = Wikipedia | date = December 28, 2007 | url = http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coeducation | accessdate = 2008-12-16 | archive-date = 2008-12-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081204082510/http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coeducation | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==歷史==
[[File:Hathorn_Hall_(extended).jpg|thumb]] 
1855年成立時，緬因州立神學院（Maine State Seminary，貝茨學院的前身）是新英格蘭第一所男女共學的學院<ref name=":21">{{Cite web|url=http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/bates-college-2036|title=Bates College {{!}} Best College {{!}} US News|website=colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com|access-date=2016-06-16|quote=Bates College [is] the first coeducational college in New England.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083505/http://colleges.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-colleges/bates-college-2036|archivedate=2016-03-04|df=}}</ref><ref name=":31">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/colleges/bates-college/|title=Bates College|website=Forbes|access-date=2016-06-16|quote=[Bates College] was the first coeducational college in New England.|archive-date=2016-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601085209/http://www.forbes.com/colleges/bates-college/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，作為廢奴主義者成立的學院，第一批學生中就有數名前奴隸。<ref name="autogenerated3">{{Cite web |url=http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-2/ |title="Race relations at Bates College" |accessdate=2015-02-03 |archive-date=2017-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627160626/http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 創始人是美國政治家歐仁·貝爾班克·切尼（Oren Burbank Cheney）<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?vid=0sJkkT9w7iRYiZPNsLPwM6r&id=LkEOAAAAIAAJ&pg=RA1-PA771&lpg=RA1-PA771&dq=%22parsonsfield+seminary%22&as_brr=1 Maine: a history - Maine Historical Society, American Historical Society - Google Boeken<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。學院拒絕具有排外性質的[[兄弟會和姐妹會|兄弟會和姐妹會]]<ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-4/|title=Chapter 4 {{!}} 150 Years {{!}} Bates College|website=www.bates.edu|accessdate=2015-11-23|archive-date=2015-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151217164403/http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，切尼請他的朋友、美國參議員[[查尔斯·萨姆纳|查尔斯·萨姆纳]]為學院寫下校訓<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bates.edu/communications/brand-identity-guide/|title=Brand Identity Guide {{!}} Communications {{!}} Bates College|website=www.bates.edu|access-date=2016-06-09|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602044807/http://www.bates.edu/communications/brand-identity-guide/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title = Chapter 1 {{!}} 150 Years {{!}} Bates College|url = http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-1/|website = www.bates.edu|accessdate = 2015-11-24|archive-date = 2015-12-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151217164342/http://www.bates.edu/150-years/history/progressive-tradition/chapter-1/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2005年，《[[普林斯顿评论|普林斯顿评论]]》称贝兹学院是美国大学中“最有价值的大学之一”。Elaine Tuttle Hansen在2002年成为贝兹学院第七位校长。从她擔任校长起，贝兹学院兴建了新教学楼，新餐厅，新宿舍楼等等。这些都是环保建筑。贝兹学院是绿色能源领导俱乐部（Green Power Leadership Club）的成员之一，该学校所使用的能源中占比96%的部分来自可再生资源。

==录取==
贝兹学院的新生录取率約為22%<ref name=":17">{{Cite web|url=http://www.bates.edu/research/files/2017/01/bates.facts_1617.pdf|title=Bates College Common Data Set 2017|last=|first=|date=|website=|access-date=|archive-date=2017-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171007121033/http://www.bates.edu/research/files/2017/01/bates.facts_1617.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。从1984起，新学生不需提交SAT成绩为录取条件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bates.edu/about-admissions.xml |title=Bates College {{!}} Admissions<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-12-16 |archive-date=2008-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207193510/http://www.bates.edu/about-admissions.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

